2) Prompt families (paraphrase invariance)

For each operator, make 10 paraphrases that mean the same move.

Example вҖңReframeвҖқ paraphrases:

вҖңReinterpret this in a more constructive lightвҖқ

вҖңShow a different way to view thisвҖқ

вҖңTurn this into a learning opportunityвҖқ

вҖңHow else can we frame this?вҖқ

3) Topic crossing (content invariance)

Pick 5 topics (AI safety, relationships, career, politics, health) and apply each operator to each topic prompt.

So: 10 operators Г— 10 paraphrases Г— 5 topics = 500 operator turns (thatвҖҷs already plenty).

